        "<p>When she</p>\n<p>was halfway across the room there came a great shriek from the wind,</p>\n<p>and the house shook so hard that she lost her footing and sat down</p>\n<p>suddenly upon the floor.</p>\n<p>Then a strange thing happened.</p>\n<p>The house whirled around two or three times and rose slowly through the</p>\n<p>air.</p>\n",
